high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter then turn left and walk to the counter then turn left.
Look up and open the second cabinet from the left and grab the dirty plate then close the door.
Turn around and walk to the sink on your left then turn left to face it.
Wash the plate in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Turn left and walk to the counter then turn left and walk all the way to the shelves in the corner on the wall in front of you.
Put the plate to the left of the salt.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean plate on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn around, go forward, hang a left and go to the counter to the right of the stove.
Take the dirty plate out of the second top cabinet to the right of the stove.
Turn around, go forward to the sink on the left.
Put the plate in the sink and rinse it off, then pick it back up.
Turn to the left, go to the counter, hang a left and go to the brown shelf across the room.
Put the plate on the second shelf to the left of the salt.
anns.task_desc: Put clean plate on a shelf.

wash and remove plate from sink
